>> source: Julia Turshen's What Goes with What
>> serves: 4
>> total time: 5 minutes
>> image: Pizzeria Vinaigrette.jpg
>> tags: vegan, gluten-free, dairy-free, salad, dressing

Place @extra-virgin olive oil{1/3%cup}, @red wine vinegar{3%Tbsp}, @kosher salt{1/2%tsp}, @dried oregano{1/2%tsp}, and minced @garlic clove{1%small} in a #bowl and whisk well to combine (or combine everything in a #jar, screw on the lid, and shake vigorously, then store in the jar). Store for up to a ~{1%week} in a covered container (or jar) in the refrigerator.
